00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:41.950
That means they lose
some of their stickiness.

00:06:41.950 --> 00:06:43.727
If you want your post-it notes to stick,

00:06:43.727 --> 00:06:45.660
well then just start at one side,

00:06:45.660 --> 00:06:47.590
and pull the note to the opposite side.

